<plot>Widescreen avant*garde is a program which discusses the international Independent-, Arthouse-, Experimental- and Trash-Cinema. The host Fabian Hübner presents in eight episodes exceptional films and their directors. Avant*garde celebrates pop cultural film-buff clichés tongue-in-cheek and takes the viewer on an entertaining and informative cinematic expedition.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052329</url></doc>
